---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Writings
permalink: /writings/
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Writings
  order: 30

---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero writings-hero">
  <div class="hero-body">
    <div class="container has-text-centered p-6" style="background-color: rgba(51, 46, 99, 0.33);">
      <h1 class="title has-text-white">Writings</h1>
      <p class="subtitle has-text-white">A collection of articles and insights from technology to life experiences.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Introductory Paragraphs -->
<div class="container">
  <div class="notification is-light is-size-5 mb-5" style="background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px;">
    <p>Welcome! Here you'll find a growing library of personal essays, technical guides, and reflections on creativity, resilience, and the digital world. Each article is written to inspire, inform, and encourage youâ€”whether you're seeking practical advice or a moment of connection.</p>
    <p>Browse the latest posts or explore by category. I hope these writings spark new ideas, offer comfort, and help you feel a little less alone in your journey. Dive in and join the conversation!</p>
  </div>



  <!-- Content Section -->
{% set categories = collections.writingsByCategory | keys | sort %}
{% for category in categories %}
  {% set articles = collections.writingsByCategory[category] %}
    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="title is-4">{{ category | capitalize }}</h2>
      <div class="columns is-multiline">
        {% for article in articles %}
          {% set formattedPublishDate = article.data.publishedDate | formatDate %}
          {% if (not article.data.publishedDate) or (formattedPublishDate <= currentDate) %}
          <div class="column is-one-quarter">
            <div class="card is-flex is-flex-direction-column">
              {% if article.data.image %}
              <div class="card-image">
                <figure class="image">
                  <img src="{{ article.data.image }}" alt="{{ article.data.title }}" loading="lazy" style="object-fit: cover; height: 200px;">
                </figure>
              </div>
              {% endif %}
              <div class="card-content">
                <p class="title is-5">
                  <a href="{{ article.url }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a>
                </p>
                <p class="subtitle is-6">
                  <span class="icon is-small is-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-calendar"></i>
                  </span>
                  {{ article.date | dateDisplay }}
                </p>
                <p class="content-preview">{{ article.data.description }}</p>
                {% if article.data.tags %}
                <div class="tags mt-auto">
                  {% for tag in article.data.tags %}
                    <span class="tag is-primary is-light">{{ tag }}</span>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
{% include "partials/newsletter-cta.njk" %}

<style>
  .card {
    height: 100%;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .card-image figure {
    margin: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .card-content {
    flex-grow: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .content-preview {
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .title.is-5 a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .title.is-5 a:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .tags {
    margin-top: auto;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .tag {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .column.is-one-quarter {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
